message:
We love seeing this! It’s going to take our communities and our neighbors to help end human trafficking. Without community we are not nearly as effective. When people take a stand against trafficking we are lending a voice to those who don’t have one. 
#realmen #takeastandagainsttrafficking 

#Repost @motojt
・・・
I've been blessed to participate in many ways in the fight against slavery. I didn't know what to do. I didn't know how to do it. However, when I was asked, I did something. 

I've had a part in changing lives... Saving people from their captors and helping others into recovery. When I'm lying on my deathbed, this will not be a regret.

#noregrets #noregretsjustlove #endchildtrafficking  #endchildsextrafficking #endslavery #helperase #helperasechildtrafficking
